* Signal Conditioner AC Analysis (LM741)
* Bode plot: gain and phase vs frequency

VCC VCC 0 12
VEE VEE 0 -12

* AC source: 1V amplitude for dB reading directly
VIN N_IN 0 AC 1

* Stage 1: Non-inverting amplifier (G=11)
R6 N_IN 0 100k
XU1 N_IN FB1 VCC VEE STAGE1 LM741_NS
R1 STAGE1 FB1 100k
R2 FB1 0 10k


* Sallen-Key LPF
R3 STAGE1 N1 10k
R4 N1 N2 10k
C3 N1 0 33n
C4 N2 FILTERED 15n

* Stage 2: Unity-gain buffer
XU2 N2 FILTERED VCC VEE FILTERED LM741_NS

* Load
R5 FILTERED 0 10k

* Model
.SUBCKT LM741_NS    1   2  99  50  28
*
*Features:
*Improved performance over industry standards
*Plug-in replacement for LM709,LM201,MC1439,748
*Input and output overload protection
*
****************INPUT STAGE**************
*
IOS 2 1 20N
*^Input offset current
R1 1 3 250K
R2 3 2 250K
I1 4 50 100U
R3 5 99 517
R4 6 99 517
Q1 5 2 4 QX
Q2 6 7 4 QX
*Fp2=2.55 MHz
C4 5 6 60.3614P
*
***********COMMON MODE EFFECT***********
*
I2 99 50 1.6MA
*^Quiescent supply current
EOS 7 1 POLY(1) 16 49 1E-3 1
*Input offset voltage.^
R8 99 49 40K
R9 49 50 40K
*
*********OUTPUT VOLTAGE LIMITING********
V2 99 8 1.63
D1 9 8 DX
D2 10 9 DX
V3 10 50 1.63
*
**************SECOND STAGE**************
*
EH 99 98 99 49 1
G1 98 9 5 6 2.1E-3
*Fp1=5 Hz
R5 98 9 95.493MEG
C3 98 9 333.33P
*
***************POLE STAGE***************
*
*Fp=30 MHz
G3 98 15 9 49 1E-6
R12 98 15 1MEG
C5 98 15 5.3052E-15
