.ENDS

* AC sweep: 10 Hz to 100 kHz, 50 points per decade
.ac dec 50 10 100k

.control
run
wrdata sig_cond_ac.txt vdb(FILTERED) vp(FILTERED) vdb(STAGE1) vp(STAGE1)
quit
